A new cartoony gungame map!  

Archaeologist have discovered a temple hidden in the mountains the only problem?  It's been controlled by aliens disguised as terrorists!  Counter-Terrorist forces have been sent in to eliminate the alien threat and retake the temple!

all files are packed in the .bsp 

map contains buyzones if you wish to play with bots which is probably the worst idea ever because bots are literally useless to do the rounded hill in ct spawn and teleporters which make it fun for normal people
